<$button class="api-summary-btn" set="$:/state/api-daiso-image-1" setTo="yes">
<span class="api-method api-post">POST</span>
<span class="api-path">/api/books/images/upload</span>
<span class="api-summary-text">이미지 단일 업로드</span>
<span class="api-chevron">▶</span>
</$button>
